Description.SourceString: Long-feared on the open seas, Titan-Class battleships are spoken of in hushed tones and with great reverence. Fitted with a wide arsenal of cannons and gun emplacements, the Titan’s enemies will soon feel the crushing depths. The Republic Coastal Legion holds Titans as its Signifiers and entire fleets rally on their position. Modelled on the flagship of Ambrose Leon’s storied fleet, the Titan is a beacon of victory for the Mesean people.
